Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.33,0:00:04.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喧嚣学院 稍后即将播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.85,0:00:06.94,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年C班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅津茂雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于田径部 17岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最近开始交了个女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.98,0:00:14.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.16,0:00:16.77,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同属田径部的两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.88,0:00:18.86,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从暑假开始交往的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展非常顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.03,0:00:23.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他却有个烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢接吻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.47,0:00:30.58,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睁睁地看着不断出现的机会溜走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是没勇气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.66,0:00:34.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天的运动会不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.21,0:00:36.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在她面前展现出我的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋起来一定就会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.02,0:00:40.20,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了 小圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.90,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赌上了这场胜负 绝对要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.74,0:00:45.58,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.49,0:00:51.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪 有猪闯进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.85,0:00:53.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂雄被猪给绊倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.98,0:00:59.57,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 茂雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.07,0:01:02.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆 对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不能怪你啦 都怪那头猪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.51,0:01:06.55,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.85,0:01:09.35,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是想表现给她看 然后跟她接吻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.91,0:01:11.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么丧气啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.84,0:01:13.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定有机会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.85,0:01:15.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生组很强的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.58,0:01:16.77,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有你在啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我有件事情想拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.33,0:01:24.35,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我拿到第一名 亲我一下当奖励好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.74,0:01:31.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我困扰了这么久 小圆竟然..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小圆拿第一是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.13,0:01:39.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不算什么奖励了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.98,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易小圆给我机会 我竟然还这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.23,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要当成奖励吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来我就不会输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我出场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.46,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.40,0:02:05.95,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.55,0:02:12.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿破仑 你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.92,0:03:43.01,sub2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的战斗 / 男人的战斗 / 战斗结束之后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.01,0:03:47.01,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(610,330)}冠\N军\N花\N落\N谁\N家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.01,0:03:47.01,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(30,330)}就\N看\N男\N女\N接\N力\N赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.01,0:03:50.02,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(610,280)}第\N四\N棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.01,0:03:50.02,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(30,280)}泽\N近\N\N爱\N理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.02,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,280)}播\N磨\N\N拳\N儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.02,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(30,260)}不\N跑\N吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.19,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心点哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.56,0:04:07.62,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还真忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.52,0:04:11.11,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在骑马战中受伤的孩子真不少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.49,0:04:12.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于告一段落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.80,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有人受伤啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.64,0:04:22.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.59,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在骑马战中受伤了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:32.88,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来干吗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.78,0:04:38.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实受了一点点小伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.58,0:04:40.10,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没什么大碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.25,0:04:43.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 想要点膏药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.49,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…又不好意思特别麻烦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.68,0:04:50.02,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才犹豫要不要进来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你大可不必介意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.81,0:04:56.54,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能先让我看看伤口吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待会儿要参加大队接力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.12,0:05:00.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得先把伤势处理好才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.72,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟第一次碰面时的感觉不太一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在哪里见过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她完全不记得了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没把我放在眼里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.16,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那一次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.03,0:05:26.73,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在这把哈里欧压倒在床上的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.19,0:05:27.90,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.87,0:05:31.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪你会觉得我怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.10,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完全是个意外哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.54,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为好久没见哈里欧了 所以当时很感动哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.49,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 哈里欧是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是播磨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.86,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 已经习惯这样叫他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.81,0:05:51.35,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师您和播磨认识吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.23,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.60,0:05:59.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间的关系 不是三言两语能讲清楚的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.44,0:06:08.96,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之呢 就像我是房东 他是住户之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.19,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.10,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.35,0:06:19.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄错了吗 感觉你好像在吃醋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.41,0:06:28.16,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么啊 吃醋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.67,0:06:31.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 只是有点在意而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.83,0:06:36.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校内有名的不良少年和新任美女保健老师有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人在意也很正常吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.37,0:06:44.54,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女保健医生吗 真不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来蛮响亮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了 时间要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.29,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口不要紧了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.44,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这膏药 我带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.39,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.96,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 您真的很亲切哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.43,0:07:05.16,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系 您不用替我担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:08.79,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.94,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下来是班级对抗接力赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.18,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子二年级组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.42,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.50,0:07:18.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场决战 C班220分 D班218分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.78,0:07:19.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负的关键 就在这场战斗上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将成为争夺冠军的最大关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.12,0:07:34.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 比赛开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.62,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴 加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在领先的是C班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.03,0:07:45.39,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐拉大了差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.15,0:07:46.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三原…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.50,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快的已经交给第二棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C班的三原速度好快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样能把D班给甩开吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛 播磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.01,0:08:10.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这头猪跑进赛道所以才害我受伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.77,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你替我去跑接力赛也是应该的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.47,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛不痛啊 拿破仑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.85,0:08:16.71,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没受伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有在听啊 播磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 拜托你了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.38,0:08:23.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 我不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你去你就去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.07,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来 你为什么要在学校里养猪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去告老师的 你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.94,0:08:31.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.54,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪也好长颈鹿也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.66,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爷爱在哪儿养就在哪儿养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.02,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚远点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C班的嵯峨野惠 依然领先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.31,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四棒是泽近爱理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C班能独占鳌头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.51,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能就此认输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.12,0:09:00.64,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.90,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽近选手好快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.20,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她美丽的外貌完全相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.30,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说她跑起来就像外表一样华丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.95,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽近真厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.59,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理应该能跑得再快些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚受伤了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.82,0:09:32.10,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 泽近在刚才的骑马战中摔了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里欧 不 她和播磨是同一组吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.29,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才她到保健室来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.40,0:09:42.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她说没什么大碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.02,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真有点替她担心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是那时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是刮了我胡子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.88,0:09:59.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算她活该 对吧 拿破仑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.29,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喂一下这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.41,0:10:10.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.35,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快支撑不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.92,0:10:13.59,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.17,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚好重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.47,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会撑不下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.67,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.99,0:10:19.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不想输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.43,0:10:39.42,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接力棒呢 接力棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.82,0:10:51.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没什么大碍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.30,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦 这么点小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理 真替你担心呢 不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看男子接力赛吧 马上要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先不去了 想在这里稍微呆一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.98,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我再过去 谢谢你 天满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.20,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一会儿见哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.72,0:11:46.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 我替你赢回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就扯平了 懂了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.28,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会终于要接近尾声了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.94,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子接力赛开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级现在是D班领先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.44,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其后C班以5分之差紧追不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.06,0:12:09.73,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想赢就要跑第一才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 肯定会赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了的话我们来玩惩罚游戏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.58,0:12:18.42,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在运动员们进场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.40,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.88,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小美琴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.89,0:12:30.64,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.73,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑马战你扯了后腿 这次可要雪耻喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.29,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是故意的 还记着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.58,0:12:45.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 谢谢你在骑马战时保护了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说赢了就亲我吗 小美琴你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思啦 你这白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.17,0:12:58.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 我们会给你加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.39,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.44,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子太狡猾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.57,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么时候处的这么好的 可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.49,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.84,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云 看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.65,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 播磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.79,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 影武者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.84,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天满在看着我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.77,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云 天满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.16,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.51,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 那两个白痴的脸色迷迷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点干劲都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点紧张感都没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.55,0:13:36.18,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 他们就是这种人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:40.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 C班 不知为何他们军心涣散啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的家伙们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.96,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红颜祸水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.62,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们终究也只是一群废物而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.14,0:13:51.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他们是强敌呢 抬举他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.88,0:14:04.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 接力赛和个人赛完全是两码事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就传授必胜的策略给你们 用心听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接力赛的关键就在于接棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.57,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要提前计算好递棒的时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:18.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道得挺多的嘛 今鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.20,0:14:21.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很意外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.94,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要靠接力赛来洗刷骑马战的污名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.57,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我正要说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.72,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔也是会认真的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.03,0:14:33.20,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了这场 我们就是英雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨 最后一棒就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对谁说话呢 你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.12,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大材小用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.80,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.80,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.93,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决赛开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.08,0:15:10.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊 不愧是D班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.42,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这种不知名的家伙都这么强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:15.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D班领先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.68,0:15:19.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着是C班接棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.17,0:15:26.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快 麻生选手超过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.28,0:15:27.95,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.21,0:15:29.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙搞什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.10,0:15:37.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今鸟选手 做出了短跑的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.43,0:15:40.44,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信这家伙 我真够白痴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.80,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿什么嘿 你这笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.18,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间摔到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.86,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上不断翻滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.29,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这时又跑了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.73,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是作战计划吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.09,0:15:58.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗 以翻滚起跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.71,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后借助惯性加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落到最后了 最后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.47,0:16:05.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全失算啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.54,0:16:08.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个差距来看我们赢定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是我和波摩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.16,0:16:11.96,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.33,0:16:15.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东乡 别小看我们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.32,0:16:20.22,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们吗 你很看重播磨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.88,0:16:24.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我等太久啊 我这个人没耐性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.66,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今鸟选手终于到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.27,0:16:31.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你要把棒递过来啊 今鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.19,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级回转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹够了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.90,0:16:38.96,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花井选手 好快的速度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼般的表情 风神降临了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.55,0:16:51.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 花井正在接近我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然感到压力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 集中精力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我们还在领先 下一棒是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.36,0:17:03.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.85,0:17:12.23,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗 后来居上才是最棒的胜利方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 日本武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.33,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是影武者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这发型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.92,0:17:26.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 要是跑着跑着 帽子掉了怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.55,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.08,0:17:34.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接棒 我们的男子汉之魂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.56,0:17:38.65,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜 你小子真不会替别人着想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.41,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.16,0:17:45.77,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.97,0:17:47.11,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨干劲十足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨好快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人刮目相看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么拼命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 播磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的班级也在为他喝彩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.65,0:18:05.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再快一点 趁帽子掉下来之前冲过终点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越跑帽子越往后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.74,0:18:17.22,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 我有生以来第一次向你祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.34,0:18:21.35,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予我奇迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.54,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终点到了 播磨拳儿获得了第一名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.73,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C班赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.86,0:19:04.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗结束后 我们还是和睦相处的校友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.81,0:19:07.11,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么凑人数太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是班委的义务吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此华丽 真是令人吃惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.50,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.58,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌丸呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.30,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来乌丸要负责放音乐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.07,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家似乎都对我视而不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.32,0:19:58.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心地跳着奥克拉荷马土风舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.77,0:20:04.73,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 这样一来也不用隐藏我的光头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.27,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变得独自一人了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.85,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 这很适合不良少年的我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.00,0:20:21.86,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来跳舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.19,0:20:24.53,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 你说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.03,0:20:28.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚伤了 而我又是光头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.92,0:20:30.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么可害羞的
